# FlyRank Capstone Rules

## Stack
- React 19
- Vite
- JavaScript (ES6+)
- ESLint
- CSS (`src/index.css` for global styles and `src/App.css` for component styles)

## Commands
- Use `npm run dev` to start the development server.
- Use `npm run build` to create a production build.
- Run `npm run lint` before committing changes.

## Code Style
- Use functional React components only.
- Keep components small and reusable.
- Place reusable components in `src/components/`.
- Use meaningful variable and function names.
- Keep commits in Conventional Commits format (e.g., `feat: add welcome page`).

## Do Not
- Commit `node_modules/`.
- Add unnecessary dependencies without approval.
- Modify generated files unless required.